Author: erisaki
Text: I see, that makes sense. Thank you!

Author: BladderPatrol
Text: It’s the frequency! People that throw up via purging typically do it more often and consistently throughout their lives than someone that is just sick or pregnant with morning sickness. If you had an ongoing sickness that made you puke a bunch the doctor would probably discuss the damage is doing to your body with you, but if it’s just regular ‘I’m sick occasionally’ puking then it’s not really a big deal.
